@startuml
actor User as "Customer/Support/Admin"
participant "API Client" as API
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "AuthService" as AS
participant "UserRepository" as UR

User -> API: Enter username and password
API -> AC: POST /login {username, password}
AC -> AS: Validate credentials
AS -> UR: Fetch user by username
UR --> AS: Return user data
AS --> AC: Generate JWT if valid
AC --> API: Return JWT or error
API --> User: Display login success or failure
@enduml
